	<td align="left"><b><font face="Arial" color="#FFFFFF">Warning!</font></b></td>
	<td align="right"><b><font color="white">12/06/02 8:16 am</font></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr bgcolor="white">
	<td colspan="2" bgcolor="white">
	<font color="#0d014d">
	If you haven't come across this yet, you need to know that Foilage Shield bugs casters self invis. If you cast FS on a caster who is self invised it will drop their invis completely. The dangerous part of this is that it leaves the invis buff icon up on the caster so that they think they are still invisible. /poke VI - Fix this please!	<br><br>
	Posted By Seriena	</td>
	</tr>
	
	</table>	

