	<td align="left"><b><font face="Arial" color="#FFFFFF">Forums are open again</font></b></td>
	<td align="right"><b><font color="white">12/03/02 7:33 pm</font></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr bgcolor="white">
	<td colspan="2" bgcolor="white">
	<font color="#0d014d">
	Thanks to the generosity of EZboard supporters and those that contributed directly to TDG all of the forums are available to everyone once again. /cheer  We've also started a new forum dedicated to druid Alternate Advancement. <a href=http://pub149.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm41>Check it out</a>.<br><br>

In other news, if you haven't heard there is a patch scheduled for tomorrow. Cross your fingers in hopes that VI has been listening to the many <a href=http://pub149.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showMessage?topicID=29744.topic>threads</a> across all class boards regarding issues players have with PoP. The biggest concerns seem to be the lack of content available to 63+ players as well as the low spell drop rate on parchments over 63+ spells. We shall see....	<br><br>
	Posted By Seriena	</td>
	</tr>
	
