	<td align="left"><b><font face="Arial" color="#FFFFFF">TDG Forums</font></b></td>
	<td align="right"><b><font color="white">11/08/02 9:26 am</font></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr bgcolor="white">
	<td colspan="2" bgcolor="white">
	<font color="#0d014d">
	This community has grown a lot over the past year and as a result the cost to keep the forums going with EZBoard has also risen. So, TDG has made the decision to lock the forums under the <b>The Druids Grove</b> and <b>The Ruins</b>. Only EZBoard supporters will be able to view and post in these forums. <b>The Circle</b> forums are still open to everyone. Read this <a href=http://pub149.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showMessage?topicID=29509.topic>post</a> for more information.<br><br>

	<br><br>
	Posted By Seriena	</td>
	</tr>
	
