	<td align="left"><b><font face="Arial" color="#FFFFFF">Bugs</font></b></td>
	<td align="right"><b><font color="white">11/06/02 8:06 am</font></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr bgcolor="white">
	<td colspan="2" bgcolor="white">
	<font color="#0d014d">
	Our visitors have found a few bugs that need to be fixed. By posting this here, I'm hoping you will all /bug report and feedback these items:<br><br>

-Affliction Efficiency IV and Affliction Haste IV are currently only working on spells lower than 60<br><br>
-Spirit of Wood prevents clerics from using Divine Barrier. This may be intended by VI, but it seems rather ridiculous to keep these two spells from stacking. So, do a /feedback if nothing else. <a href=http://pub149.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showMessage?topicID=29513.topic>Click here for the thread</a>	<br><br>
	Posted By Seriena	</td>
