	<tr>
	<td align="left"><b><font face="Arial" color="#FFFFFF">New Editorial at The Druids Grove</font></b></td>
	<td align="right"><b><font color="white">08/21/02 11:11 am</font></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr bgcolor="white">
	<td colspan="2" bgcolor="white">
	<font color="#0d014d">
	Miss Foxfyre has posted an editorial up at the grove.  Please check the editorial button on the left to read this well written piece.
