	<tr>
	<td align="left"><b><font face="Arial" color="#FFFFFF">EQ at Gen Con</font></b></td>
	<td align="right"><b><font color="white">06/27/02 9:58 am</font></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr bgcolor="white">
	<td colspan="2" bgcolor="white">
	<font color="#0d014d">
	This years <a href=http://www.wizards.com/default.asp?x=gencon>Gen Con</a> will take place August 8-11th. Among all the other games going on, there will be daily EQ competitions starting at 11 am. The first event will be a Warrior vs. Warrior battle to the death using equal items. The second event will give you and your friends a chance to compete as a team in a 3 on 3 Gladiator Competition. 

There will be 8 classes to choose from, all equipped with Epic weapons and equal armor items. You may use 1 of each class to make up your team of 3 to participate in this event. 

The winners of each of these events will win a one-year free subscription to EverQuest and Gladiator Championship Rings for their play character, as well as your picture with "The Gladiator" in the Ring of Champion's section of our Gen Con 2002 web page.

Read VI's official announcement <a href=http://eqlive.station.sony.com/events/gencon_2002.jsp>here</a>.

	<br><br>
	Posted By Seriena	</td>
	</tr>
	
	</table>	

