	<td align="left"><b><font face="Arial" color="#FFFFFF">EQ Subscription Services Downtime</font></b></td>
	<td align="right"><b><font color="white">06/14/02 5:39 pm</font></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr bgcolor="white">
	<td colspan="2" bgcolor="white">
	<font color="#0d014d">
	From Developers Corner:<br><br>
On Wednesday the 19th at 3:00 AM PDT the EverQuest subscription services will be unavailable for about 6 hours due to a systems upgrade.<br>
<br>
During this time customers will not be able create new accounts, upgrade to new services or change their subscription information in any way.<br>
<br>
This downtime will not affect gameplay. Customers will be able to log in and play as usual. It will only affect subscription services as mentioned above.<br>
<br>
Thank you for playing EverQuest.<br>
<br>
- The EverQuest Team	<br><br>
	Posted By Iallaas	</td>
	</tr>
	
