	<tr>
	<td align="left"><b><font face="Arial" color="#FFFFFF">Patch Message</font></b></td>
	<td align="right"><b><font color="white">02/13/02 5:02 pm</font></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr bgcolor="white">
	<td colspan="2" bgcolor="white">
	<font color="#0d014d">
	A few worthy notes from today's patch:


-Many higher level NPCs now have a random delay before they initially spawn. This means that they will appear at a more random time interval after servers or zones are brought up. This is designed to provide a fairer distribution of these NPCs across all time zones 

-Egress should once again force a 'zone' to clear aggro

-several NPCs in many zones have been given the 'animal' tag

View full patch message at: http://eq.castersrealm.com/viewarticle.asp?Article=4099	<br><br>
	Posted By Cobbyl	</td>
	</tr>
	
	</table>	

